O ' Charley ' s names CEO Gregory Burns chair . O ' Charley ' s Inc said Tuesday its board of directors had given the company ' s chief executive officer , Gregory Burns , the additional responsibilities of chairman and president . It said the board also gave the secretary and treasurer , Chad Fitzhugh , the additional title of chief financial officer . A company spokeswoman said Fitzhugh would replace Burns as chief financial officer , a post that he had to give up in order to take on his new reponsibilities . She said Burns , who has been chief executive officer since 1994 , would replace Charles McWhorter , who resigned earlier this month to pursue other business interests . O ' Charley ' s operates 69 casual dining restaurants in 10 U . S . states including Ohio and Tennessee . 
